First Department,

February, 1950.

(February 7, 1950.) The People of the State of New York ex rel. New York Central Railroad Company, Appellant, against Harry B. Chambers et al., Constituting the Tax Commission of the City of New York, et al., Respondents. [Property Bounded by Leight & Other Streets, Borough of Manhattan.]

No opinion. Settle order on notice. Present- — Dore, J. P., Cohn, Callahan, Van Voorhis and Shientag, JJ.
